<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b4Mar1931"><font color="red">4 March 1931</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from T.S. Eliot to Paul L&eacute;on): Ask &hellip; Babou &hellip; permission &hellip; one shilling edition of HAVETH CHILDERS EVERYWHERE &hellip; end of this month or beginning of April. Our publication date is Thursday. </div>
